  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Oshi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a ringing voice, an illusory melody of your voice to make contact with a creature whom you've heard speak before that is on the same plane of existence as you. As a part of the casting of this jutsu, the nearest functioning communication device within 100 feet of the target begins to ring with a tune of your choice. If there is no suitable device close enough to the target, this jutsu fails.</p><p>The target must make a Charisma saving throw, being compelled to answer your call on a failure and gaining 1 rank of Charmed, or becoming able to ignore the call on a successful save. Once the connection is established, the call is crystal clear and cannot be dropped until the conversation has ended or the jutsu's duration ends. You can end the conversation at any time, but the target must succeed on a Charisma saving throw as an action to end the conversation.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost by 3. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank or higher, it applies another rank of Charmed on a failure and no longer requires a functioning communication device, instead being able to create the call sound entirely in the target's mind.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
